songs.title: Open Bar (Freestyle)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Check it, check it
This is Open Bar with Logic
Under Pressure the album is out now
Liftoff, Power 106
Open Bar, four bars, four topics
You cool with that?
Open Bar, Logic, best night of your life
The first topic is: best night of your life

[Verse 1]
Best night of my life, yeah I gotta get it like this
You know it was on Power 106
Live for the whole crowd, for the whole world
Don't need your girl homie, got my own girl, get it

[Interlude]
Open bar, four bars, four topics with Logic
Liftoff, Power 106
Nas' Illmatic

[Verse 2]
Illmatic, yeah we still at it
Did I drop it I don't know, they gon' call it, Under Pressure
I need the more, nah never the lesser
This is how we do it, uhh cause I'm so fresher
Feelin' good, I think it's longer than them four bars
But it doesn't matter, homie I got four cars, feelin' yeah

[Interlude]
Open bar, four bars, four topics with Logic in here
The album Under Pressure, Open Bar
Being biracial

[Verse 3]
I kinda have some mixed feelings on that issue homie
Yeah, black and white it's kinda crazy
It's funny how people can perceive you
But it doesn't really matter cause I gotta get the preview with these lyrics so
If you really wanna know cop the album Under Pressure
For the real, not the lesser, what's up

[Interlude]
One more topic, Open Bar
Four bars, four topics with Logic, J. Cruz, Justin Credible
Going platinum

[Verse 4]
Goin' platinum, man it seems like it never happens
Unless you Taylor Swift
Man I gotta be extra swift, with the real
Yeah I gotta do it, this is how we feelin' homie
I'm tryin' to make it to the ceiling homie
Yeah, hundred thousand in a week, maybe, maybe not
It doesn't matter cause it's all about the fans and the Rattpack is all we got, yeah
